astro-ph/0512105 [abs, ps, pdf, other] :

          Title: Multiplicity-Study of Exoplanet Host Stars
          Authors: M. Mugrauer, R. Neuhuser, T.Mazeh, E. Guenther
          Comments: 3 pages, 1 figure
          We  carry  out a systematic search campaign for wide companions
          of  exoplanet  host  stars  to study their multiplicity and its
          influence on the long-term stability and the orbital parameters
          of  the  exoplanets.  We  have already found 6 wide companions,
          raising  the  number  of confirmed binaries among the exoplanet
          host  stars  to  20  systems.  We  have  also searched for wide
