          This is a review talk on the UV and infrared selected galaxies.
          The  central  question addressed is: do UV and infrared surveys
          see  the  2  sides of star formation of the same population, or
          star  formation of 2 different populations? We first review the
          literature  on  the  UV  and IR selected galaxy samples, try to
          quantify   the   difference  and  overlaps  between  these  two
